fields.title: Sidebar
fields.content: The sidebar menu is your main source of navigation.\nHere you can find and navigate to all the different pages in the application.

fields.title: The Dashboard Page
fields.content: The dashboard page is like your home page, your starting page.\nThere are two main features to notice on the dashboard...

fields.title: Map
fields.content: The first feature is the map. This map shows all the existing nodes in your network and where they are located.\nFeel free to scroll around the map and look for Ocean View!

fields.title: Node Information
fields.content: The second feature shows basic, yet important overview information about the nodes.\n4 important pieces of node information health are given
